   <body>
      <p>When a user is unavailable or unable to perform tasks in <ph href="../../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/>, you can transfer all that user's tasks to other users. The users to whom the tasks are transferred to can then perform the associated tasks and workflow actions of the transferer.</p>
      <p>Using the<uicontrol>DELEGATION OF AUTHORITY</uicontrol>form, you can delegate tasks of one user to another user with the same role in <ph href="../../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/> for specific projects.<note> Only users with the<uicontrol>Administrator</uicontrol> role can perform these activities.</note>
      </p>
      <p>You can perform the following tasks:</p>
